OL,3,CGirl's message in bottle travels from
OL,4,CSunderland to Sweden
OL,6,FA 12-year-old girl was "over the moon"
OL,7,Fafter discovering her message in a
OL,8,Fbottle was found in Sweden less than a
OL,9,Fyear after it was thrown off a pier in
OL,10,FSunderland.
OL,12,FGrace Liddle, then 11, and her brother
OL,13,FHarry Liddle, now six, threw glass
OL,14,Fbottles from filled with hand-written
OL,15,Fscrolls, which included their names
OL,16,Fand contact details for their mother,
OL,17,Foff Roker Pier in Sunderland, Tyne and
OL,18,FWear, on 28 August 2023.
