OL,3,CGirl's message in bottle travels from
OL,4,CSunderland to Sweden
OL,6,FOn 6 March, their mother Christie
OL,7,FBowley, 35, received a response on
OL,8,FMessenger to say Harry's bottle had
OL,9,Fbeen found in Denmark.
OL,11,FWhile Grace was happy for her brother,
OL,12,Fshe longed for the day her bottle
OL,13,Fwould be found, but was losing hope.
OL,14,FHer mother told the PA news agency:
OL,15,F"Grace was convinced hers sank and had
OL,16,Ftaken a room up in the Titanic."
