OL,4,CSunderland to Sweden
OL,6,FOn 3 August, Ms Bowley, who helps out
OL,7,Fat her partner Jason Liddle's
OL,8,Fbusiness, Instaflor Ltd, and lives
OL,9,Fwith her family in Grindon Lane,
OL,10,FSunderland, opened Messenger and saw a
OL,11,Fnote from a man called Freddy
OL,12,FStahlberg, who said he found Grace's
OL,13,Fbottle on an island in Sweden called
OL,14,FPinno.
