OL,4,CSunderland to Sweden
OL,6,FMr Stahlberg, 72, who lives in
OL,7,FGrebbestad during the summer months
OL,8,Fand in Lund for the rest of the year,
OL,9,Ftold PA when he discovered the bottle
OL,10,Fon 2 August, he initially found it
OL,11,Fhard to read the message inside as it
OL,12,Fhad been in salt water for a prolonged
OL,13,Fperiod of time.
OL,15,F"Our family tried our best to find
OL,16,Fwords that were useful, and we were
OL,17,Ffinally able to identify Christie's
OL,18,Fname, a hint that she had a Facebook
OL,19,Faddress, as well as the word
OL,20,FSunderland," he said.
