OL,3,CGirl's message in bottle travels from
OL,4,CSunderland to Sweden
OL,6,F"With her name, I found her Facebook
OL,7,Fpage, and looking at the images there
OL,8,FI could deduce that she lived in
OL,9,FSunderland, which was mentioned in the
OL,10,Fmessage in the bottle.
OL,12,F"With this information at hand, I
OL,13,Fdared to send a message to Christie.
OL,15,F"She replied some time later and we
OL,16,Fwere all very enthusiastic about
OL,17,Fhaving solved the riddle."
