OL,3,CGirl's message in bottle travels from
OL,4,CSunderland to Sweden
OL,6,F"They've both been found in the space
OL,7,Fof a year, you wouldn't expect them to
OL,8,Fbe found so soon ` I think it just
OL,9,Fshows how small the world actually is.
OL,11,F"I just think it's a miracle,
OL,12,Fconsidering how big the sea is."
OL,14,FMs Bowley said she initially thought
OL,15,Fthere was "no chance" of the bottles
OL,16,Fever being discovered further than the
OL,17,Fpier, because when her children first
OL,18,Fthrew them out to sea, they started
OL,19,Fheading back to shore.
