OL,4,CSunderland to Sweden
OL,6,FShe added the similar names of the
OL,7,Fpeople who found the bottles made the
OL,8,Fsaga more entertaining.
OL,10,F"Harry's bottle was found by a man
OL,11,Fcalled Frederik and Grace's was found
OL,12,Fby someone called Freddy ` it is just
OL,13,Fmad," she said.
OL,15,FShe hopes she can take Harry and Grace
OL,16,Fto the locations their bottles were
OL,17,Ffound and the family has considered
OL,18,Fthrowing more bottles into the
OL,19,FAtlantic Ocean to see if they end up
OL,20,Fin the United States.
